    "zhCN": "以一个移动动作，魂刃可以以灵能塑形出一把由她思想铸造的半固态念刃\n魂刃必须在1级决定念刃的形态．她可以选择将之塑形为一件轻型武器，一把单手武器，亦或是双手武器。一旦决定了造型，以后当她塑形念刃时她的念刃都会以这一形态出现。轻型武器形态可以造成1d6点伤害，单手武器形态可以造成1d8点伤害，双手武器可以造成2d6点伤害。以上的所有伤害都是以中型生物挥舞的中型武器计算的，根据不同的体型大小调整你的武器伤害。不论是那一种形态，念刃的重击范围都是19-20/X2。如果你的魂刃是大体型生物或是小体型生物，你可以根据她的体型来调整念刃的伤害骰。如果魂刃选择将她的念刃塑形为轻型武器，那她可以选择在显形念刃时显现2把轻型武器造型的念刃。如果她这么做的话她承受标准的双武减值。\n不论魂刃以何种形态塑形她的念刃，念刃本身并没有固定的伤害类型。当她显形念刃并向其中灌注能量时，魂刃可以选择这把念刃造成的伤害类型，钝击，挥砍，亦或是穿刺。以一个整轮动作，魂刃可以改变她现有念刃的伤害类型或者重新显形一把不同伤害类型的念刃。如果不这么做的话，念刃会一直保持上一次显形时的伤害类型。\n念刃可以被击碎（它的硬度为10并且有10点生命值），但魂刃可以用他的下一个移动等效动作重铸造一把。当魂刃松开了她紧握的念刃时，这把念刃会即时消散（除非她这么做是为了抛掷念刃，详情见下文）。一把念刃在计算DR时被视为魔法武器，同时被视为精制武器。\n如同普通武器一样，魂刃可以对念刃应用“猛力攻击”，“寓守于攻”专长。此外，她也可以选择念刃作为特殊专长的需求，比如武器专攻和精通重击。强化武器的灵能和法术也可以对念刃起效。武器娴熟也可对念刃生效，当然前提条件是这位魂刃的念刃属于轻型武器形态。\n即使在灵能无法正常作用的地方（比如位于“反灵能力场”内），通过一个20dc的意志检定，魂刃依然可以制造并维持念刃，通过这一方法显形的念刃维持等于她魂刃职业等级的轮数。当持续时间结束后，她可以通过另一个20dc的意志检定维持她的念刃，同时，在灵能无法正常作用地区，念刃被视为非魔法武器及非精制武器。如果她未能成功通过这一意志检定，那她的念刃将即时消散。于灵能无效地区，在她自己的行动回合内，魂刃可以通过一个新的意志检定（dc20）以一个移动动作重塑念刃。她在这个意志检定上获得等同于念刃增强加值的增强加值（念刃增强加值见下）。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ShapeMindBladeFeat.Name",
    "ProcessTemplates": false,
    "enGB_Base": "Shape Mind Blade",
    "zhCN": "念刃变形"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ShapeMindBladeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife’s mind blade retains the last chosen form every time it is formed until the soulknife reshapes it. If the soulknife chooses to reshape her blade, it requires a full-round action to do so. She may also re-assign the type of damage dealt as part of reshaping her mind blade if she so chooses. A soulknife can reassign the ability or abilities she has added to her mind blade; see below. To do so, she must first spend 8 hours in concentration. These cannot be the normal 8 hours used for rest, even if the soulknife does not require sleep. After that period, the mind blade materializes with the new ability or abilities selected by the soulknife.",
    "zhCN": "除非你改变念刃的造型，否则魂刃的念刃会维持上一次的显形造型。改变念刃的造型是一个整轮动作，在这一重塑过程中魂刃可以改变念刃的伤害类型。魂刃也可以通过重塑念刃来改变念刃的特殊能力（如果有的话，见下表），这一过程需要8小时的专注时间。这8小时无法用于休息，即使这位魂刃并不需要休息．经过8小时后，这把念刃的特殊能力就彻底改变了。"
  },

  // ==== CLASSES ====
  {
    "Key": "Soulknife.Name",
    "ProcessTemplates": false,
    "enGB_Base": "Soulknife",
    "zhCN": "魂刃"
  },

  {
    "Key": "Soulknife.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "Never caught unarmed, the soulknife is the literal interpretation of using the power of the mind as a weapon. Creating a mind blade is the core of the soulknife, and with it, she is a deadly combatant. Versatile and varied, the soulknife can be found in all shapes and sizes, wielding blades unique to the wielder and customized to fit the needs of the soulknife. Fluid in function, the soulknife has mastered how to alter her mind blade to fit the situation, bringing power and versatility into any combat.",
    "zhCN": "就如同字面上的意义一样，一位魂刃永远不会担心在战斗中以赤手空拳的状态迎击敌人，他们能以自身的意念来铸造兵器迎接战斗。创造一把念刃是一个魂刃最基础的核心工作，当一位魂刃手持念刃时，她便是最为致命的战士．念刃的姿态千姿多彩而绝非千人一面，你可以找到各式大小及不同形态的念刃，念刃的形态及功能会根据挥舞者的不同需求或适应使用者的个人习惯而转变。如流水般变幻形态切换功能，魂刃能根据不同的局势状况熟练的转变重塑她的念刃，以一种强大多变的方式来投入战斗。"
  },

  // ==== Added Feats====
  {
    "Key": "ExtraBladeSkill.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Extra Blade Skill",
    "zhCN": "额外魂之剑技"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ExtraBladeSkill.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "You gain an additional blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "你获得额外一个魂之剑技。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "PowerPointPool.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Power Point Pool",
    "zhCN": "灵能点池"
  },
  {
    "Key": "PowerPointPool.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "You have a pool of Power Points",
    "zhCN": "你拥有灵能点池"
  },
  {
    "Key": "PsionicBody.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Psionic Body",
    "zhCN": "灵能身躯"
  },
  {
    "Key": "PsionicBody.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "When you take this feat, you gain 2 hit points for each psionic feat you have (including this one). Whenever you take a new psionic feat, you gain 2 more hit points.",
    "zhCN": "当你选取本专长时，你每拥有一个灵能专长（包括这个），就获得2点生命值。你获得每个新灵能专长时，还可以再获得2点生命值。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "PsionicMeditation.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Psionic Meditation",
    "zhCN": "灵能冥想"
  },
  {
    "Key": "PsionicMeditation.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "You can take a move action to become psionically focused.",
    "zhCN": "你能用一个移动动作进入“灵能集中”状态。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "WildTalent.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Wild Talent",
    "zhCN": "原始天赋"
  },
  {
    "Key": "WildTalent.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "Your latent power of psionics flares to life, conferring upon you the designation of a psionic character. As a psionic character, you gain a reserve of 2 power points and can take psionic feats, metapsionic feats, and psionic item creation feats. You do not, however, gain the ability to manifest powers simply by virtue of having this feat. Additionally, you can take this feat multiple times. The first, you gain 2 additional power points, every other time, you gain only one.",
    "zhCN": "你潜在的灵能力量在你的生命中闪亮起来，你现在变为了一名灵能人物。作为灵能人物，你获得了2点灵能点而且可以选择灵能专长、超能专长和制造灵能物品专长，不过本专长本身不会给你展现异能的能力。此外，当你多次获得此专长时，首次你获得2点额外灵能点，之后每次只获得1点。"
  },
  // ==== Added Soulknife Feats====
  {
    "Key": "BladeSkillsFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Blade Skill",
    "zhCN": "魂之剑技"
  },
  {
    "Key": "BladeSkillsFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "Beginning at 2nd level and every even soulknife level thereafter, a soulknife may choose one of a number of abilities to add to her repertoire. Some blade skills have prerequisites that must be met before they can be chosen. All blade skills may only be chosen once and require the soulknife to be using her mind blade unless otherwise stated in the skill’s description.",
    "zhCN": "自2级开始，以及之后的每个偶数等级魂刃可以选择获得一个魂之剑技。其中一些魂之剑技需要一些前置条件才能选择。除非这一魂之剑技的描述中有特殊提到，否则所有魂之剑技都只能选择一次并且只有在使用念刃时才能使用。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "EnhancedMindBladeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Enhanced Mind Blade",
    "zhCN": "念刃强化"
  },
  {
    "Key": "EnhancedMindBladeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "A soulknife’s mind blade improves as the character gains higher levels. At 3rd level and every odd level thereafter, the mind blade gains a cumulative +1 enhancement bonus that she may spend on an actual enhancement bonus or on weapon special abilities. A soulknife’s level determines her maximum enhancement bonus. The soulknife may (and must, when her total enhancement is higher than her maximum bonus) apply any special ability instead of an enhancement bonus, as long as she meets the level requirements. A soulknife can choose any combination of weapon special abilities and/or enhancement bonus enhancement bonus before assigning any special abilities. If the soulknife shapes her mind blade into two items, the enhancement bonus of her mind blade (if any) is reduced by 1 (to a minimum of 0). If this would reduce the enhancement bonus on the mind blades to 0 and weapon special abilities are applied, the soulknife must reshape her mind blade to make the options valid. Both mind blades have the same selection of enhancement bonus that does not exceed the total allowed by the soulknife’s level, but she must assign at least a +1 and weapon special abilities (if any). This penalty does not apply when using the Mind Shield blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃的念刃随着魂刃的等级提高而强化．自3级开始以及之后的每个单数等级，魂刃的念刃获得1点累计的增强加值，她可以选择用来提高念刃的实际增强加值或者增添特殊能力。魂刃的职业等级决定了她念刃的增强加值上限。魂刃可以（在她的念刃增强加值已经是当前增强加值上限时是必须）选择往念刃上添加特殊能力来替代增添增强加值（只要她满足等级需求）。魂刃可以选择任意的特殊能力与不超过当前增强加值上限的增强加值组合，但是在往念刃上添加特殊特性前，念刃必须拥有至少1点增强加值。如果魂刃选择将她的念刃变形为两件物品（例如双武模式），那她的念刃的增强加值（如果有增强加值）-1（最低0）。如果念刃的增强加值降到0，那念刃上的所有特殊特性都将失效。魂刃必须重塑她的念刃来恢复特殊特性。使用以念化盾并不承受这一减值。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "FormMindBoltFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Form Mind Bolt",
    "zhCN": "念矢塑形"
  },
  {
    "Key": "FormMindBoltFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "At 1st level, as a move action, a soulbolt can form a semi-solid ranged weapon composed of psychic energy distilled from her own mind. This mind bolt appears inside of or enveloping the soulbolt’s hand.\r\nA soulbolt must choose the form of her mind bolt at 1st level. She can either form it into a short range, medium range, or long range bolt which determines the weapon’s range increment and base damage. Once chosen, her mind bolt stays in this form every time the soulknife forms her mind bolt. The long range bolt form is the smallest of forms and deals 1d6 points of damage and has a 100 ft. range increment. The medium range bolt form deals 1d8 points of damage, with a 60 ft. range increment, and the short range bolt form is the largest and heaviest form and deals 1d10 points of damage with a 20 ft. range increment. A soulbolt adds her Strength modifier to damage rolls when using the mind bolt in the short range form. All damages are based on a Medium-sized creature wielding Medium-sized weapons; adjust the weapon damage as appropriate for different sized weapons. A soulbolt with powerful build or any similar ability forms an appropriately-sized mind bolt dealing the size-appropriate amount of damage. Regardless of form, the mind bolt has a 19-20 critical threat range, has a maximum range of 10 range increments, and is treated as a projectile.\nThe form of the soulbolt’s mind bolt also determines how many hands must be used to form and manipulate the mind bolt. If the mind bolt is in long range form, both of the soulbolt’s hands remain free to hold other items such as a shield or a weapon. If the mind bolt is in medium range form, the soulbolt must have at least one hand free to form and manipulate the mind bolt. If the mind bolt is in short range form, the soulbolt must have both hands free to wield and launch the mind bolt.\n    A soulbolt can wield a buckler without penalty regardless of the form of her mind bolt.\nRegardless of the weapon form a soulbolt has chosen, her mind bolt does not have a set damage type. When shaping her weapon and assigning abilities to it, the soulbolt chooses whether it will deal bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing damage. The soulbolt may change the damage type of an existing mind bolt, or may summon a new mind bolt with a different damage type, as a full-round action; otherwise, the mind bolt retains the last damage type chosen every time it is summoned.\nThe bolt can be broken (it has hardness 10 and 10 hit points); however, a soulbolt can simply create another on her next move action. The moment she relinquishes her grip on her blade, it dissipates (unless she intends to throw it; see below). A mind bolt is considered a magic weapon for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction and is considered a masterwork weapon.\n    A soulbolt can use feats such as Rapid Shot or Precise Shot in conjunction with the mind bolt just as if it were a normal ranged weapon. She can also choose her mind bolt for feats requiring a specific weapon choice, such as Weapon Focus and Improved Critical. Powers or spells that upgrade weapons can be used on a mind bolt. The soulbolt can use feats such as Weapon Finesse that work on light weapons with her mind bolt, but such feats only work on mind bolts in a light weapon form, such as using the Mind Daggers blade skill.\nEven in places where psionic effects do not normally function (such as within a null psionics field), a soulbolt can attempt to sustain her mind bolt by making a DC 20 Will save. On a successful save, the soulbolt maintains her mind bolt for a number of rounds equal to her class level before she needs to check again, although the mind bolt is treated for all purposes as a non-magical, masterwork ranged weapon while in a place where psionic effects do not normally function. On an unsuccessful attempt, the mind bolt vanishes. As a move action on her turn, the soulbolt can attempt a new Will save to rematerialize her mind bolt while she remains within the psionics-negating effect. She gains a bonus on Will saves made to maintain or form her mind bolt equal to the total enhancement bonus of her mind bolt (see below).\nThe soulbolt chooses the appearance of her mind bolt, although its shape must reflect the selections the soulbolt has chosen: a bludgeoning mind bolt would be blunt, slashing would have an edge, etc.\nThis ability replaces the Form Mind Blade class feature normally gained by soulknives.",
    "zhCN": "1级起，以一个移动动作，魂矢可以以灵能塑形出一把由她思想铸造的半固态远程武器。念矢会在魂矢的手中或者围绕双手出现。\r\n魂矢必须在1级决定念矢的形态．她可以选择短距离、中距离或者长距离念矢来决定武器的射程和基础伤害。一旦决定了造型，以后当她塑形念矢时她的念矢都会以这一形态出现。长距离念矢尺寸最小，造成1d6点伤害并拥有100尺射程增量，中距离念矢可以造成1d8点伤害并拥有60尺射程增量，短距离念矢则是最大最重的形态，造成1d10伤害并拥有20尺射程增量。使用短距离念矢时，魂矢将自己的力量调整值加到伤害骰中。以上的所有伤害都是以中型生物使用的中型武器计算的，根据不同的体型大小调整你的武器伤害。如果你的魂矢是大体型生物或是小体型生物，你可以根据她的体型来调整念矢的伤害骰。不论是那一种形态，念矢的重击范围都是19-20/X2，拥有10点射程增量。并被视为投射物。\n念矢的形态也会影响魂矢需要用几只手来形成或操纵念矢。使用长距离念矢时，她的两只手都可以用来做别的事情。使用中距离念矢时，她必须拥有至少一只空闲手来形成和操纵念矢。使用短距离念矢时，魂矢必须使用两只空闲手来持有和发射念矢。\n魂矢可以无视她念矢的形态，在没有任何处罚的情况下装备小圆盾。\n不论魂矢以何种形态塑形她的念矢，念矢本身并没有固定的伤害类型。当她显形念矢并向其中灌注能量时，魂矢可以选择念矢造成的伤害类型，钝击，挥砍，亦或是穿刺。以一个整轮动作，魂矢可以改变她现有念矢的伤害类型或者重新显形一把不同伤害类型的念矢。如果不这么做的话，念矢会一直保持上一次显形时的伤害类型。\n念矢可以被击碎（它的硬度为10并且有10点生命值），但魂矢可以用他的下一个移动等效动作重铸造一把。当魂矢松开了她紧握的念矢时，念矢会即时消散（除非她这么做是为了抛掷念矢，详情见下文）。念矢在计算DR时被视为魔法武器，同时被视为精制武器。\n如同普通远程武器一样，魂矢可以对念矢应用“快速射击”，“精准射击”专长。此外，她也可以选择念矢作为特殊专长的需求，比如武器专攻和精通重击。强化武器的灵能和法术也可以对念矢起效。武器娴熟也可对念矢生效，当然前提条件是这位魂矢的念矢属于轻型武器形态，比如使用念刃化匕时。\n即使在灵能无法正常作用的地方（比如位于“反灵能力场”内），通过一个20dc的意志检定，魂矢依然可以制造并维持念矢，通过这一方法显形的念矢维持等于她魂矢职业等级的轮数。当持续时间结束后，她可以通过另一个20dc的意志检定维持她的念矢，同时，在灵能无法正常作用地区，念矢被视为非魔法武器及非精制武器。如果她未能成功通过这一意志检定，那她的念矢将即时消散。于灵能无效地区，在她自己的行动回合内，魂矢可以通过一个新的意志检定（dc20）以一个移动动作重塑念矢。她在这个意志检定上获得等同于念矢增强加值的增强加值（念刃增强加值见下）。\n魂矢可以决定她的念矢造型，当然这一造型必须符合念矢的伤害类型，比如钝击伤害类型的念矢必须是钝器，挥砍伤害的念刃必须有刃口，诸如此类。\n这个能力替代了魂刃的念刃塑形。"
  },
