  {
    "Key": "PsychicStrikeAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Psychic Strike",
    "zhCN": "灵能打击"
  },
  {
    "Key": "PsychicStrikeAbility.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "As a move action, a soulknife of 3rd level or higher can imbue her mind blade with destructive psychic energy. This effect deals an extra 1d8 points of damage on any attack she wishes to activate it on (as long as the attack is made with her mind blade). A soulknife may hold the charge as long as she likes without discharging. It does not go off on any attack unless she chooses to use it, and the charge is not wasted if an attack misses. Mindless creatures are immune to this damage, although non-mindless creatures immune to mind-affecting effects are affected by this damage as normal. (Unlike the rogue’s sneak attack, the psychic strike is not precision damage and can affect creatures otherwise immune to extra damage from critical hits or more than 30 feet away.) A mind blade deals this extra damage only once when this ability is called upon, but a soulknife can imbue her mind blade with psychic energy again by taking another move action. Additionally, she may recharge it as a swift action by expending her psionic focus.\nOnce a soulknife has prepared her blade for a psychic strike, it holds the extra energy until it is used (whether the attack is successful or not). Even if the soulknife drops the mind blade (or it otherwise dissipates, such as when it is thrown), it is still imbued with psychic energy when the soulknife next materializes it.\nIf the soulknife forms her mind blade into two weapons, she may imbue each mind blade with psychic strike as normal. If she reshapes her mind blade into a single weapon form, the additional psychic strike imbued into the additional weapon is lost. At every four levels thereafter (7th, 11th, etc), the extra damage from a soulknife’s psychic strike increases by 1d8.",
    "zhCN": "自3级开始，魂刃可以以一个移动动作向她的念刃灌注毁灭性的灵能力量．这可以使她的一次攻击造成额外1d8伤害（她可以指定任意一次攻击，只要这次攻击是由她念刃造成的）。魂刃可以保持这一充能状态。除非魂刃在攻击中使用了灵能打击，否则这一充能状态会一直维持，而且充能状态不会因攻击失手而消失．无心智生物对灵能打击的额外伤害免疫，尽管他们依然会承受正常伤害．（不同于游荡者的偷袭，灵能打击不属于精准伤害，可以伤害那些没有明确身体结构而对重击免疫或者距离超过30尺的生物。）1次充能只能造成一次额外伤害，但魂刃可以以另一个移动动作对念刃进行充能．此外魂刃可以通过耗费灵能集中来以迅捷动作进行充能。\n一旦魂刃选择对念刃进行灵能打击的充能，这一充能状态会一直保持到使用为止（不论攻击是否成功）。即使魂刃将念刃抛弃或者进行投掷攻击，在下次显形念刃时念刃依然维持充能状态。\n如果魂刃选择显形双武器形态的念刃，她可以和正常状态一样对念刃灌注灵能。如果她再将念刃塑形为单件武器形态，那灌注在另一件武器上的灵能就会消失。自3级之后每4级（7级，11级，以此类推），灵能打击增加1d8额外伤害。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "PsychicStrikeFreeAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Psychic Strike (Swift)",
    "zhCN": "灵能打击（迅捷）"
  },
  {
    "Key": "SoulknifeBonusFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Soulknife Bonus Feat",
    "zhCN": "魂刃额外专长"
  },
  {
    "Key": "SoulknifeBonusFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife may choose Power Attack, Two-Weapon Fighting, or Weapon Focus (mind blade) as a bonus feat at 1st level.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃在1级时可以从猛力攻击、双武器战斗、武器专攻（魂刃）中选择一项作为额外专长。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "SoulknifeKinetBlastFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Weapon Focus (Mind Blade)",
    "zhCN": "武器专攻（魂刃）"
  },
  {
    "Key": "SoulknifeKinetBlastFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "You gain a +1 {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} on all {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attack rolls{/g} you make using your mind blade.",
    "zhCN": "使用魂刃进行的所有{g|Encyclopedia:Attack}攻击检定{/g}均获得+1{g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}加值{/g}。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "SoulknifeQuickDraw.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Quick Draw",
    "zhCN": "即时备战"
  },
  {
    "Key": "SoulknifeQuickDraw.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "A 5th level soulknife may manifest her mind blade as a free action, though she may still only attempt to do so once per round (unless throwing the weapon multiple times using the Multiple Throw blade skill).",
    "zhCN": "自5级开始，魂刃可以以一个自由动作显形念刃，尽管她一回合依然只能显形一把念刃（除非是使用暴雨梨花这一剑技进行复数念刃投掷，她可以显形复数的念刃）。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ThrowMindBladeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Throw Mind Blade",
    "zhCN": "念刃投掷"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ThrowMindBladeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "All soulknives have some knowledge of how to throw their mind blades, though the range increment varies by form and the largest of blade forms cannot be thrown. Light weapon mind blades have a range increment of 20 ft. One-handed weapon mind blades have a range increment of 15 ft. Two-handed weapon mind blades cannot be thrown without the Two-Handed Throw blade skill. Whether or not the attack hits, a thrown mind blade then dissipates.",
    "zhCN": "所有的魂刃都精擅于投掷念刃，尽管射程增量受限于念刃的造型，而且那些大型的念刃无法投掷。轻型武器造型的念刃的射程增量为20尺，单手武器为15尺，大型念刃无法投掷，除非拥有对应剑技。无论攻击是否命中，念刃都会在投掷之后消失。"
  },  
  {
    "Key": "ThrowMindBladeAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Throw Mind Blade",
    "zhCN": "念刃投掷"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ThrowMindBladeAbility.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "All soulknives have some knowledge of how to throw their mind blades, though the range increment varies by form and the largest of blade forms cannot be thrown. Light weapon mind blades have a range increment of 20 ft. One-handed weapon mind blades have a range increment of 15 ft. Two-handed weapon mind blades cannot be thrown without the Two-Handed Throw blade skill. Whether or not the attack hits, a thrown mind blade then dissipates.",
    "zhCN": "所有的魂刃都精擅于投掷念刃，尽管射程增量受限于念刃的造型，而且那些大型的念刃无法投掷。轻型武器造型的念刃的射程增量为20尺，单手武器为15尺，大型念刃无法投掷，除非拥有对应剑技。无论攻击是否命中，念刃都会在投掷之后消失。"
  },  
  // ==== Added Soulknife Blade Skills====
  {
    "Key": "AlterBladeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Alter Blade",
    "zhCN": "剑式莫测"
  },
  {
    "Key": "AlterBladeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife gains the ability to shape her mind blade into different weapon forms. She may change her blade’s form to the light weapon, one-handed weapon, or two-handed weapon forms any time she forms her mind blade. Additionally, the soulknife may choose to form her mind blade into a one-handed weapon and a light weapon instead of two light weapons.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃获得将自己念刃变形转化为另一种武器的能力。她可以在显现念刃时将念刃的形态转化为轻型武器，单手武器，或者是双手武器，无论她的念刃的原型是何种武器。如果一位魂刃的念刃是两把轻型武器，那她可以选择将之转化为一把轻型武器和一把单手武器。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "BladeRushFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Blade Rush",
    "zhCN": "刀锋舞步"
  },
  {
    "Key": "BladeRushFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife rushes forward with a dash of incredible speed. As a Swift action, the soulknife may expend her psionic focus and move up to her speed without provoking attacks of opportunity. The soulknife must be at least 6th level in order to select this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃以不可置信的速度向前方冲锋。以一个迅捷动作，魂刃可以消耗她的灵能集中移动等于其速度的距离，而不会引发借机攻击。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少6级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "BladeRushAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Blade Rush",
    "zhCN": "刀锋舞步"
  },
  {
    "Key": "BladeRushAbility.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife rushes forward with a dash of incredible speed. As a Swift action, the soulknife may expend her psionic focus and move up to her speed without provoking attacks of opportunity. The soulknife must be at least 6th level in order to select this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃以不可置信的速度向前方冲锋。以一个迅捷动作，魂刃可以消耗她的灵能集中移动等于其速度的距离，而不会引发借机攻击。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少6级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "BladestormAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Bladestorm",
    "zhCN": "剑刃风暴"
  },
  {
    "Key": "BladestormAbility.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "As a full attack, when wielding her mind blade, the soulknife can give up her regular attacks and instead throw one mind blade at her full attack bonus at all opponents within 30 feet, ignoring the normal range increments for throwing a mind blade. Regardless of the number of attacks she makes, she only provokes attacks of opportunity as though she made a single ranged attack. The soulknife must possess the Bladewind blade skill to take this ability, this ability may not be used if the mind blade is in a two-handed weapon form, and the soulknife must be at least 16th level to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "以一个整轮动作，魂刃可以选择放弃她的普通攻击，以她完整的基础攻击加值对30尺内所有对手投掷一把念刃，这一攻击忽视正常情况下念刃投掷的射程增量。无论这一行动造成了几次攻击次数，使用剑刃风暴被视为一次远程远程攻击因而只提供一次借机攻击机会。选择这一魂之剑技需要魔刀千刃及至少16级魂刃等级。魂刃无法在使用双手武器模式念刃的状况下使用这一魂之剑技。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "BladewindAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Bladewind",
    "zhCN": "魔刀千刃"
  },
  {
    "Key": "BladewindAbility.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife gains the ability to momentarily fragment her mind blade into numerous identical blades, each of which strikes at a nearby opponent. As a full attack, when wielding her mind blade, a soulknife can give up her regular attacks and instead fragment her mind blade to make one melee attack at her fullbase attack bonus against each opponent within reach. Each fragment functions identically to the soulknife’s regular mind blade. When using bladewind, the soulknife can choose to expend her psychic strike if an attack misses to reroll that attack, but none of the bladewind attacks deal any extra damage from psychic strike. When using bladewind, a soulknife forfeits any bonus or extra attacks granted by other feats or abilities (such as Cleave or haste). The mind blade immediately reverts to its previous form after the bladewind attack. A soulknife must be at least 8th level to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃可以选择将她的念刃炸裂产生无数致命的剑刃碎片，来对附近的对手产生强烈的打击。当显形她的念刃时，魂刃可以选择放弃她的通常攻击以一个整轮动作将她的念刃炸裂对来所有触及内的对手进行一次猛烈攻击，这一攻击采取她的正常攻击加值。每一片碎片的伤害的都采取这位魂刃通常的念刃伤害。当使用魔刀千刃时，魂刃可以选择消耗灵能打击充能，来在攻击失手的时候重掷攻击骰，但这一行为并不会带来额外伤害。当使用魔刀千刃的时候魂刃放弃其他所有额外攻击的机会（比如加速或顺势斩）。在攻击结束后念刃会迅速恢复原本的形态。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少8级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "BladewindSpendPsionicStrikeAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Bladewind Spend Psionic Strike",
    "zhCN": "魔刀千刃（消耗灵能打击）"
  },
  {
    "Key": "BladewindSpendPsionicStrikeAbility.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "As part of a Bladewind attack, a Soulknife can opt to use their Psychic Strike to reroll a missed attack, rather than for damage.",
    "zhCN": "魔刀千刃攻击时，魂刃可以选择消耗灵能打击充能，来在攻击失手的时候重掷攻击骰，但这一行为并不会带来额外伤害。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DazzlingBladeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Dazzling Blade",
    "zhCN": "炫目之锋"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DazzlingBladeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife may, as a standard action, channel psionic energy into her mind blade, dazzling all creatures within 30 feet. A successful Fortitude save negates this effect. The save DC is 10 + the soulknife’s base attack bonus.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃能使用一个标准动作，将灵能灌入念刃，使得30尺内生物进入目眩状态。强韧豁免成功能免除这个效果。豁免DC为10+魂刃的基础攻击加值。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DeadlyBlow.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Deadly Blow",
    "zhCN": "死风过境"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DeadlyBlow.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife’s mind blade critical multiplier increases by 1. A soulknife must be at least 10th level to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃的念刃重击倍数增加1。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少10级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DispellingStrikeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Dispelling Strike",
    "zhCN": "解法强袭"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DispellingStrikeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "With this blade skill, the soulknife is capable of channeling her psychic strike damage into caustic, anti-psionic energy. As a standard action, the soulknife can expend her psionic focus and her psionic strike to make an attack with her mind blade (or equivalent weapon). If it hits, it deals weapon damage as normal, and the soulknife affects the target with a targeted dispel psionics power as a psilike ability, with a manifester level equal to her class level. The soulknife does not apply the expended psychic strike’s damage to her attack. The soulknife must be 8th level to select this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "使用此魂之剑技，魂刃能够将她的心灵打击伤害转化为腐蚀性的反灵能。用一个标准动作，灵魂之刀可以消耗掉他的灵能集中和灵能打击，用她的念刃（或同等武器）进行一次攻击。如果命中，它会像正常情况一样造成武器伤害，同时魂刃的目标受到如同对目标施放的驱散灵能影响，显能等级等于她的职业等级。魂刃不会对这次攻击施加消耗的心灵打击的伤害。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少8级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DisruptingStrikeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Disrupting Strike",
    "zhCN": "腐化强袭"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DisruptingStrikeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "As a full-round action, a soulknife can make one melee attack against each enemy adjacent to her. If she hits, the attack deals no damage, but each enemy hit takes a -5 penalty to all melee and ranged damage rolls until the start of the soulknife’s next turn. This blade skill may not be used with the mind bolt.",
    "zhCN": "使用整轮动作，魂刃可以对一个邻接的敌人进行单次攻击。如果命中，该次攻击不会造成伤害，但是敌人在所有的近战和远程攻击伤害骰中都会受到-5减值，直到魂刃的下一轮开始。这个剑技不能用魂矢发动。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DisruptedBuff.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Disrupted",
    "zhCN": "腐化强袭"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DisruptedBuff.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "Target takes a -5 penalty to all melee and ranged damage rolls.",
    "zhCN": "目标在所有的近战和远程攻击伤害骰中都会受到-5减值。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DuelingBladeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Dueling Blade",
    "zhCN": "决斗剑锋"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DuelingBladeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "When a soulknife is fighting defensively, or using the Combat Expertise feat, with a mind blade, and an opponent misses her in melee, she may expend her psionic focus to make an attack of opportunity against that opponent with her mind blade.",
    "zhCN": "当魂刃使用防御式战斗或者寓守于攻专长时，如果有对手对其近战攻击失手，她可以消耗掉灵能集中，使用魂刃对攻击者发动一次借机攻击。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DuelingBladeAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Dueling Blade (Toggle)",
    "zhCN": "决斗剑锋（切换开关）"
  },
  {
    "Key": "EnhancedRange.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Enhanced Range",
    "zhCN": "射程增量"
  },
  {
    "Key": "EnhancedRange.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife’s range increment when throwing her mind blade in any form doubles.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃的所有形态念刃投掷射程增量加倍。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ExpandShieldFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Expand Shield",
    "zhCN": "念盾延展"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ExpandShieldFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "When using the total defense action or attacking defensively, as a free action on her turn the soulknife can transform her mind shield into a tower shield until the start of her next turn. All of the standard penalties for having a mind shield shaped as a tower shield apply. The soulknife must have the Mind Shield blade skill to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "使用全力防御或者防御性战斗时，以一个自由动作，魂刃可以将她的念盾化为塔盾形态，直到她的下一轮开始。魂刃会受到所有塔盾的标准减值。魂刃必须拥有以念化盾剑技才能选择此剑技。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ExplodingCriticalFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Exploding Critical",
    "zhCN": "势如破竹"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ExplodingCriticalFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "When a soulknife confirms a critical hit, she can expend her psionic focus to deal her psychic strike damage, even if her mind blade was not charged with psychic strike, and even if she already dealt psychic strike on the attack. a soulknife must be at least 12th level to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "当一位魂刃成功确认重击时，她可以选择耗费灵能集中充能灵能打击造成额外伤害。即使重击时她还未进行灵能打击充能或是已经在攻击时使用了灵能打击。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少12级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "FireBladeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Fire Blade",
    "zhCN": "炽热灼锋"
  },
  {
    "Key": "FireBladeSpendFocusAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Fire Blade (Spend Focus)",
    "zhCN": "炽热灼锋（消耗灵能集中）"
  },
  {
    "Key": "FireBladeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "When the soulknife makes an attack with her mind blade, she can choose to have it deal fire damage instead of its normal damage. In addition, the soulknife can expend her psionic focus when she hits with an attack to deal an additional +1d10 fire damage. The soulknife must be at least 8th level to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃使用念刃攻击时，可以选择让其造成火焰伤害来替代通常的伤害。此外，魂刃可以在攻击命中时消耗掉灵能集中，造成额外1d10火焰伤害。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少8级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "FullEnhancement.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Full Enhancement",
    "zhCN": "剑质天成"
  },
  {
    "Key": "FullEnhancement.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "When forming her mind blade into multiple items, the soulknife suffers no reduction in enhancement bonus.",
    "zhCN": "当将她的念刃转化为多把时，魂刃不必承受任何增强减值。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "GruesomeRiposteFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Gruesome Riposte",
    "zhCN": "极恶反击"
  },
  {
    "Key": "GruesomeRiposteAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Gruesome Riposte (Toggle)",
    "zhCN": "极恶反击（切换开关）"
  },
  {
    "Key": "GruesomeRiposteFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife may expend her psionic focus as an immediate action to attack an enemy who has successfully struck her in melee. This attack is assumed to happen after the successful attack, so she cannot use this ability if the attack would put her below 0 hit points, nor does dropping her enemy below 0 hit points prevent the attack from hitting. A soulknife must be at least 10th level to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "当对手以一个近战攻击命中魂刃时，魂刃可以选择耗费灵能集中以一个直觉动作对敌手进行攻击。这一攻击必须在对手攻击结束后才能展开，因而使用这一剑技时魂刃的生命值不能低于0，否则无法使用这一剑技，你也无法通过反击把对手的生命值降低到0以下来避免其攻击。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少10级魂刃等级."
  },
  {
    "Key": "IceBladeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Ice Blade",
    "zhCN": "凛冬冰锋"
  },
  {
    "Key": "IceBladeSpendFocusAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Ice Blade (Spend Focus)",
    "zhCN": "凛冬冰锋（消耗灵能集中）"
  },
  {
    "Key": "IceBladeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "When the soulknife makes an attack with her mind blade, she can choose to have it deal cold damage instead of its normal damage. In addition, the soulknife can expend her psionic focus when she hits with an attack to reduce the target’s speed by half until the end of the soulknife’s next turn. The soulknife must be at least 8th level to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃使用念刃攻击时，可以选择让其造成寒冷伤害来替代通常的伤害。此外，魂刃可以在攻击命中时消耗掉灵能集中，使得敌人的速度减半，直到魂刃的下一轮。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少8级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ImprovedEnhancement.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Improved Enhancement",
    "zhCN": "增强强化"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ImprovedEnhancement.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife’s enhancement bonus on her mind blade increases by 1. This increase may be used to increase the actual enhancement bonus of the mind blade (to a maximum of +5) or be spent on weapon special abilities, as normal. A soulknife must be at least 12th level to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃的念刃增强加值加1，这一加值可以转化为实际的增强加值（最高＋5）或者用来添加特殊能力。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少12级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ImprovedMindShield.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Improved Mind Shield",
    "zhCN": "念盾强化"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ImprovedMindShield.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The shield bonus to AC granted by the soulknife’s mind shield increases by 1. The soulknife must have the Mind Shield blade skill in order to select this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "念盾提供的AC上的盾牌加值增加1。魂刃必须拥有以念化盾剑技才能选择此剑技。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "LaunchMultibolt.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Launch Multibolt",
    "zhCN": "多重念矢"
  },
  {
    "Key": "LaunchMultibolt.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife gains the benefits of the Manyshot feat. The soulknife must possess the Launch Mindbolt class feature to select this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃获得多重射击专长的效果。魂刃必须拥有发射念矢的职业特性才能选择此剑技。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "LightningBladeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Lightning Blade",
    "zhCN": "霹雳雷锋"
  },
  {
    "Key": "LightningBladeSpendFocusAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Lightning Blade (Spend Focus)",
    "zhCN": "霹雳雷锋（消耗灵能集中）"
  },
  {
    "Key": "LightningBladeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "When the soulknife makes an attack with her mind blade, she can choose to have it deal electricity damage instead of its normal damage. In addition, the soulknife can expend her psionic focus when she hits with an attack to give the target a -2 penalty to attack and damage rolls until the end of her next turn. If the target is wearing metal armor, the penalty increases to -3. The soulknife must be at least 8th level to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃使用念刃攻击时，可以选择让其造成电击伤害来替代通常的伤害。此外，魂刃可以在攻击命中时消耗掉灵能集中，使得目标在攻击和伤害骰上获得-2减值，直到魂刃的下一轮。如果目标穿着金属盔甲，该减值增加到-3。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少8级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "MindBladeFinesse.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Mind Blade Finesse",
    "zhCN": "念刃娴熟"
  },
  {
    "Key": "MindBladeFinesse.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "Mind Blade Finesse: The benefits of the Weapon Finesse feat apply to the mind blade even when it is in forms that cannot normally be the subject of Weapon Finesse (including two-handed forms).",
    "zhCN": "念刃可以享受到武器娴熟的效果，即使其原本的形态通常并不能获得武器娴熟的效果（包括双手武器形态）。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "MindShield.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Mind Shield",
    "zhCN": "以念化盾"
  },
  {
    "Key": "MindShield.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife gains a +2 shield bonus to armor class, as long as she has a hand free.",
    "zhCN": "在有空闲手时，魂刃在AC上获得+2盾牌加值。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "PowerfulStrikes.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Powerful Strikes",
    "zhCN": "猛力强袭"
  },
  {
    "Key": "PowerfulStrikes.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife’s psychic strike deals an additional 1d8 damage.",
    "zhCN": "灵能打击造成1d8额外伤害。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "PsionicTraining.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Psionic Training",
    "zhCN": "灵能训练"
  },
  {
    "Key": "PsionicTraining.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "Gain a psionic feat instead of selecting a blade skill. The soulknife must meet all prerequisites of the psionic feat selected. She may not select the feat Extra Blade Skill with this blade skill. This blade skill may be selected multiple times.",
    "zhCN": "获得一项灵能专长来替代剑技。魂刃需要满足对应专长的前置条件。她不能选择额外额外魂之剑技。该剑技可以选择多次。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ReachingBladeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Reaching Blade",
    "zhCN": "如意锋刃"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ReachingBladeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife may expend her focus to increase her reach with her mind blade by 5 feet until the start of her next turn. Unlike normal reach weapons, a soulknife may also attack adjacent opponents with her mind blade. A soulknife must be at least 8th level to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃可以选择耗费灵能集中使她的念刃增加5点触及范围直到她下一轮的开始。不同于其他长型武器，魂刃依然可以使用念刃攻击邻近单位。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少8级魂刃等级．
"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ReapersBladeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Reaper's Blade",
    "zhCN": "收割刀锋"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ReapersBladeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "A soulknife with this ability automatically recharges her psychic strike ability if she reduces an enemy’s hit points to below 0 with a melee attack using her mind blade. A soulknife must be at least 10th level to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "拥有这一剑技的魂刃可以在使用念刃将一个敌人的生命值降到0以下时进行自动重新为灵能打击能力。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少10级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "RendingBlades.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Rending Blades",
    "zhCN": "撕皮剔骨"
  },
  {
    "Key": "RendingBlades.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "Hooks extend from the soulknife’s mind blade, dealing an additional 1d6 bleed damage on a critical hit.",
    "zhCN": "给念刃添加额外的倒钩，在重击时造成额外1d6流血伤害。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "TelekineticBolt.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Telekinetic Bolt",
    "zhCN": "心灵念矢"
  },

  {
    "Key": "TelekineticBoltShort.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Telekinetic Bolt (Short)",
    "zhCN": "心灵念矢（短距离）"
  },
  {
    "Key": "TelekineticBoltMedium.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Telekinetic Bolt (Medium)",
    "zhCN": "心灵念矢（中距离）"
  },
  {
    "Key": "TelekineticBoltLong.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Telekinetic Bolt (Long)",
    "zhCN": "心灵念矢（长距离）"
  },
  {
    "Key": "TelekineticBolt.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife learns to manifest her mind blade as a variety of ranged weapons as well as the forms her mind blade normally may take. Selection of this blade skill grants the form mind bolt and launch mind bolt class features (see soulbolt archetype). The soulknife is always considered proficient with her mind bolt. The mind bolt gains the enhancement bonus of the soulknife’s mind blade and may select its own enhancements (such as distance or flaming) as if it were a separate weapon from her mind blade. The soulknife may now also take soulbolt specific blade skills. This cannot be taken if you possess the form mind bolt class feature previously. The soulknife must be at least 4th level to select this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃学会了将念刃塑形为多种远程武器的方法。选择该剑技会获得念矢塑形和发射念矢职业特性（如同变体职业魂矢）。魂刃总会被视为擅长其念矢。念矢获得如同念刃的强化并且可以选择一部分独有的特性（比如远距或炽焰），如同其是一把独立武器。魂刃也会同样获得魂矢专用的魂之剑技。如果你已经拥有了念矢塑形则无法选择此剑技。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少4级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ThunderBladeFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Thunder Blade",
    "zhCN": "轰鸣音锋"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ThunderBladeSpendFocusAbility.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Thunder Blade (Spend Focus)",
    "zhCN": "轰鸣音锋（消耗灵能集中）"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ThunderBladeFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "When the soulknife makes an attack with her mind blade, she can choose to have it deal sonic damage instead of its normal damage, although the damage of the attack is halved. In addition, the soulknife can expend her psionic focus when she hits with an attack to stagger the target until the end of her next turn unless the target makes a successful Fortitude save (DC 10 + the soulknife’s base attack bonus). The soulknife must be at least 8th level to choose this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃使用念刃攻击时，可以选择让其造成音波伤害来替代通常的伤害，然而伤害会减半。此外，魂刃可以在攻击命中时消耗掉灵能集中，使得目标恍惚，除非其通过强韧检定（DC为10+魂刃的基本攻击加值）。选择这一魂之剑技需要至少8级魂刃等级。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "TowerMindShieldFeat.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Tower Mind Shield",
    "zhCN": "念化塔盾"
  },
  {
    "Key": "TowerMindShieldFeat.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife’s mind shield can be shaped into a tower shield. Altering the mind shield in this fashion is a move action that does not provoke attacks of opportunity. The mind shield remains in this form until shaped back into its standard form. The mind shield is treated in all ways (except visually) as a masterwork tower shield, granting a +4 shield bonus to AC, imposing a +2 Maximum Dexterity Bonus, a -9 armor check penalty, and a 50% arcane spell failure chance. The soulknife must have the Mind Shield blade skill to select this blade skill.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃的念盾成为塔盾形态。以这种方式改变念盾形态是一个移动动作但是不会引起借机攻击。念盾将保持这种形态，直到再次被塑形为标准形态。念盾在所有方面（视觉上除外）都被视为精制品塔盾，在AC上给予+4盾牌加成，同时获得+2最大敏捷加值，-9护甲检定减值，以及50%奥术失败率。魂刃必须拥有化念为盾剑技才能选择此剑技。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "TwoHandedThrow.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Two-Handed Throw",
    "zhCN": "双手投掷"
  },
  {
    "Key": "TwoHandedThrow.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "The soulknife gains the ability to throw her mind blade if it is in two-handed form, with a range increment of 10 ft.",
    "zhCN": "魂刃获得可以投掷双手武器模式的念刃的能力，射程增量为10尺。"
